### Hex Memory Map ###
 Legend:
  - = Unused memory
  F = Filled ROM
  S = Stored serial code
  A = Stored ASCII string
  R = Reserved for checksum
  C = Stored checksum result
  T = Trailing code
  & = Find & replace opcode
  X = Find & delete opcode
  1 = one by one decending led blinking.hex
